  "name": "Carom Shot",
  "shortName": "carom-shot",
  "description": "<i>Carom Shot</i> is a 3D billiards game with four different gameplay modes; story mode, pocket game, carom game, and speed. Story mode uses visual-novel style for dialogues between characters and the story is set in stages. In order to finish each stage you need to win several times and reach necessary amount of money to proceed further. Pocket game is 1 or 2 player game where player gets to select one of the nine available character (three of which are locked at the beginning) and one of the three game types; NineBall, Rotation, or EightBall. Carom game additionally lets the player set the number of lost points for a handicap, and game types available change to FourBall, ThreeBall, and 3-Cushion. Finally, in the Speed mode your only opponent is the time you try to beat by quickly finishing all the tasks presented.",
